name: noaa-esri-grid-seafloor-hardbottom-occurrence-predictions-model-in-new-york-offshore-planning-9445c
notes: This dataset represents hard bottom occurrence predictions from a spatial model developed for the New York offshore spatial planning area. This model builds upon the data compilation and analytical framework laid out by Greene et al. (2010). The model also provides a continuous gridded prediction surface representing the likelihood of hard bottom occurrence.
